content.overview-desc: The Carousel page showcases the Carousel component, which allows you to create dynamic and interactive image carousels or slideshows.
content.how-to-desc: Import the Carousel component, and provide the images or content that you want to display within the carousel as child components. Customize the carousel behavior and appearance using the provided props.
